---

## UiSystem-G8 UiSystem-G8: View State Persistence Across Refresh
**Status:** in_progress
**Priority:** P1
**Milestone:** M1 - UI State Management
**Module:** ui-system
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:ui-system
**Depends on:** UiSystem-A5

### Implementation Status ✅ VERIFIED


All success criteria verified:
- ✅ useViewState composable provides reactive currentView with localStorage persistence
- ✅ Automatic state restoration on initialization
- ✅ Automatic state persistence on view changes via Vue watch
- ✅ Robust validation of stored view IDs with cleanup of invalid data
- ✅ Error handling for localStorage unavailability (private browsing, quota exceeded)
- ✅ Full test coverage: 11/11 unit tests passing
- ✅ Code review complete: APPROVED (no issues found)
